— Governorship Primary /Senator/Reps Others, May 18- 26 ABUJA – The All Progressives Congress APC has finally released the timetable and schedule of activities leading to its special Convention where the party’s presidential flagbearer will be unveiled. The special Convention holds May 30 through June 1st in Abuja. The Convention is to be preceded by the Governorship primaries (May 20th), State Assembly primaries(22nd), Federal House of Reps (24th) and Senatorial (26th ), while the various Appeals hold between 22nd -24 th May.. Meanwhile the party has fixed the sale.of forms to begin Tuesday April 26th and end May 6th 2022.Last day of submission of forms has been fixed for 10th.